{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ada61327d7","title":"关于要少讲空话多讲办法的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ce30b84213","index":0,"year":1959,"month":3,"day":20,"articleId":"ada61327d7"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"41d329127e","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"ada61327d7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央办公厅1959年3月17日编印的《情况简报》（六级干部会议专辑）第四十八号上。这辑简报登载了中央办公厅曹幼民发自济南的一封信，信中介绍了山东省六级干部会议对公社管理体制、积累和消费的比例、今年小麦的分配、粮棉油统购等政策的意见。来信还谈到，关于怎样以最快的方法向群众贯彻上述意见，山东省历城县东郊人民公社已摸到了一些经验：一是向群众贯彻得越快越有利；二是不要光摆解决思想问题的架子，而要着重把怎么办讲清楚。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b439f6b849","type":"title","text":"关于要少讲空话多讲办法的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"ada61327d7"},{"id":"41d329127e","type":"paragraph","text":"这个经验有用，可转各地。对基层干部和广大群众，要少讲空话，多讲办法。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"ada61327d7"},{"id":"cc5cdde984","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"ada61327d7"},{"id":"4ebcf86c50","type":"paragraph","text":"三月二十日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"ada61327d7"}],"page":{"id":"d08660c004","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"ada61327d7","start":374,"end":374}}}},"__N_SSG":true}